Load Public API Distribution

Source: R/select_public.R
public_Distribution.Rd

Load Public API Distribution

Usage

public_Distribution(dataset, fname = TRUE)

Arguments

dataset

<chr> dataset title

fname

<lgl> Is dataset a function name?; default is TRUE

Value

<Distribution> object

Examples

public_Distribution("utilization_provider")
